name: ABRACADABRA
description:
an ancient mystic word of unknown origin, abracadabra means "I create as I speak" and can be carried as an amulet but also as a reminder: words are spells.

*

the power is always within, available to us, and if it's not directed through a clear and conscious intention, it may then take on the obscure forms from the unconscious.


[digital remix of a nankin drawing. special edition for #WitchingHourOnHEN]
